## ðŸ©º Chest X-Ray Disease Classification  
This notebook uses a merged Chest X-Ray dataset containing three classes:

- **Normal**
- **Pneumonia**
- **Tuberculosis**

Dataset: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/muhammadrehan00/chest-xray-dataset

All images are preprocessed as RGB `.jpg` files and organized in a YOLO-style folder structure
